Bored with the usual stuffs? Then this is the one for you.Perfect! piece of gem! Complete package ! 

Breaking Bad == Superb plot + Outstanding acting by Bryan Cranston + Kickass story line + Bone-chilling moments + Unexpected twists and turns + Love + Emotions + Psychic behavior of Cranston + Comedy.

Since the day I watched First episode, Cranston has occupied special place in me because of his mesmerizing acting, I'm astonished that how a person can be so involved with his role like this.Aaron Paul's acting is really cool and you'll see the complete involvement with his role.

This TV show itself is like a drug.I was and I am highly addicted to this TV show.I feel to watch it again and again.It's impossible to take Bryan Cranston out of your mind.